The nuggos and honey, I think I've watched enough recommended vids on YouTube to notice that the Kardashians love take out so I leaned more towards her.
Beyonce was the easiest in my opinion but I wanted to shoot in the dark and chose someone that I would totally not expect.
It was easy to imagine a large Australian man, like Liam just swallowing these miniature burgers so he was my immediate choice.
I chose Kendall bc for a fact Kourtney is so known for how she eats her kitkat, so out of familiar similarities Kendall was my best choice.
And RiRi was actually the easiest bc I remember that Ellen episode.
